At the chair "Informations- und Kommunikationsdienste" at the University of Rostock a team tries to bring Bitcoin on a idsolated mobile platform.

Idea: "As BC becomes more popular it becomes a worthwhile target for attackers. As we don't focus on any fraud on [[mining]], this project aims to prevent the [[Wallet]] by creating a boxed and locked enduser wallet, that is trustworthy to the owner."

##History

* 09/2011 planing and collecting ideas
* 10/2011 evaluating different microcontroller kits

